Anti-pseudomonal and anti-endotoxic effects of surfactin-stabilized biogenic 
silver nanocubes ameliorated wound repair in streptozotocin-induced diabetic 
mice.

Krishnan N(1), Velramar B(1)(2), Pandiyan R(1)(3), Velu RK(1).

Author information:
(1)a Department of Microbiology, School of Life Sciences , Bharathidasan 
University , Tiruchirappalli , Tamil Nadu , India.
(2)b Department of Biotechnology, School of Biosciences , Periyar University , 
