of LPS-triggered expression of the TNF-α in wounds that LPS-assisted extension 
of wound repair in diabetes mellitus conditions was circumvented quite well. 
Results gathered in this study established that surfactin-stabilized AgNPs could 
effectively offer to the novel treatment of Gram-negative bacilli infection in 
diabetic wounds.

